{"_total":85,"_totalPage":9,"_page":9,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"思考","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/思考/","url":"/async/tags/思考.json","count":3}],"categories":[{"name":"思考总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/思考总结/","url":"/async/categories/思考总结.json","count":7}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/05/repost-rujingyurushi.json","date":1391529600000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":5,"name":"repost-rujingyurushi"},"subtitle":"转载自王建硕的博客","title":"【转载】入静和入世","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2014/02/05/repost-rujingyurushi/","content":"<p>本文为转载，<a href=\"http://home.wangjianshuo.com/cn/20120801_eae-3.htm\">原文地址</a></p>\n<p>本文受Paul Graham的Maker’s Schedule, Manager’s Schedule启发而作，建议大家有空去读一下。</p>\n<p>人有两种思考状态，我将一种称为入静，另一种称为入世。</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":4}],"categories":[{"name":"思考总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/思考总结/","url":"/async/categories/思考总结.json","count":7}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/02/03/new-year.json","date":1391356800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":2,"day":3,"name":"new-year"},"subtitle":"总结过去，展望未来","title":"再见，蛇年！你好，马年！","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2014/02/03/new-year/","content":"<h2 id=\"辞旧岁\">辞旧岁</h2><hr>\n<p>过年在老家闲得无聊，回头又翻了一下自己这一年来的微博，这一年来写的一些读书笔记啥的。感叹时光荏苒，岁月如梭。感觉自己进入研究生来并没有过了多久，可如今快是研二下学期了。这个2013年算是收获相当大的一年。</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":40},{"name":"jQuery","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/jQuery/","url":"/async/tags/jQuery.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"JS技术","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/JS技术/","url":"/async/categories/JS技术.json","count":13}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/01/28/jquery-resize.json","date":1390838400000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":1,"day":28,"name":"jquery-resize"},"subtitle":"使用jQuery实现","title":"使用jQuery监听DOM元素大小变化","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2014/01/28/jquery-resize/","content":"<p>今天写页面的时候突然有这么个需求，由于父元素（一个DIV）的height是由javascript计算出来的固定的值，而在其中增加了一个多说插件，在用户评论后，子元素（DIV）的height属性增加，导致子元素溢出。但是又不知道如何为多说的评论按钮增加回调函数，于是乎就想到了根据子元素的大小变化来重新计算父元素的height。</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":35}],"categories":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/CSS/","url":"/async/categories/CSS.json","count":8}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/01/09/clearfix.json","date":1389196800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":1,"day":9,"name":"clearfix"},"subtitle":"传统闭合浮动方法与使用","title":"闭合浮动最佳方案（clearfix）","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2014/01/09/clearfix/","content":""},{"tags":[{"name":"NodeJs","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/NodeJs/","url":"/async/tags/NodeJs.json","count":14},{"name":"WebIM","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/WebIM/","url":"/async/tags/WebIM.json","count":9},{"name":"WebSocket","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/WebSocket/","url":"/async/tags/WebSocket.json","count":8},{"name":"xmpp","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/tags/xmpp/","url":"/async/tags/xmpp.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"即时通信","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/categories/即时通信/","url":"/async/categories/即时通信.json","count":9}],"url":"/async/posts/2013/12/08/websocket.json","date":1386432000000,"path":{"year":2013,"month":12,"day":8,"name":"websocket"},"subtitle":"使用WebSocket+NodeJs搭建聊天室","title":"搭建HTML5简易聊天室","permalink":"http://lingyu.wang/2013/12/08/websocket/","content":"<h3 id=\"前面的话\">前面的话</h3><hr>\n<p>之前曾经写过一个符合xmpp协议的Web IM，但使用的是JSJaC，后台用的也是与之配套的jabber client，发现nodejs的事件模式更适合作为Web IM的客户端。</p>\n<p>而传统的ajax轮询机制也早晚被全双工websocket所取代，所以就打算在我的毕业设计的Web IM平台中使用websocket。</p>\n<p>在这里调研一下并作出了一个简单的版聊demo，这里讲一下这个简单demo的实现方式</p>"}]}